[[File:Badger_in_the_dark_with_reflecting_eyes.jpg|thumb]]眼睛的[[脈絡膜層|脈絡膜層]]能反射攝影師打出的光線，許多哺乳動物都有這樣的特徵]]
'''夜行瓶頸假說'''（英文：{{lang|en|Nocturnal Bottleneck Hypothesis}}）為一個假說，用於解釋許多哺乳動物的特徵行為。1942年，{{link-en|戈登·林恩·沃爾斯|Gordon Lynn Walls}}提出了夜行瓶頸假說，大多有胎盤類哺乳動物在演化史上（兩億兩千五百萬年前至六千六百萬年前的[[白堊紀﹣古近紀滅絕事件|白堊紀﹣古近紀滅絕事件]]）多屬於夜行性動物<ref>Gerkema MP, Davies WI, Foster RG, Menaker M, Hut RA. The nocturnal bottleneck and the evolution of activity patterns in mammals.  Proc Biol Sci. 2013 Jul 3;280(1765):20130508. doi: 10.1098/rspb.2013.0508</ref>。雖然部分哺乳動物在這之後演化成了日行性動物，填補了恐龍滅絕後的生態位，然後這一億六千萬年的夜行生活在解剖學特徵上留下了許多適合夜行性的演化特徵，而許多的哺乳動物如今依然仍然為夜行性<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sinn|first1=J.|title=New Study Shows Effects of Prehistoric Nocturnal Life on Mammalian Vision|url=https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2012/10/121031161025.htm|publisher=University of Texas|accessdate=24 November 2014|archive-date=2019-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905202847/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2012/10/121031161025.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==哺乳動物的演化==
[[File:Brasilitherium_riograndensis.jpg|thumb]]（''Brasilitherium''），屬於[[犬齒獸亞目|犬齒獸亞目]]，為哺乳動物的近親，可能是夜行性的穴居動物]]
<!--{{main article|Evolution of mammals}}-->
哺乳動物演化自[[犬齒獸亞目|犬齒獸亞目]]，一群外型似犬的[[合弓綱|合弓綱]]物種，崛起於[[二疊紀－三疊紀滅絕事件|二疊紀－三疊紀滅絕事件]]後。然而，同樣崛起於三疊紀的[[主龍類|主龍類]]，如[[恐龍|恐龍]]和[[鱷魚|鱷魚]]，導致了大型[[犬齒獸亞目|犬齒獸亞目]]物種的滅絕，僅剩下體型偏小的物種<ref>{{cite book|last1=Benton|first1=Michael J.|authorlink = Michael Benton|title=Vertebrate palaeontology|date=2004|publisher=Blackwell Science|location=Oxford|isbn=978-0-632-05637-8|edition=3rd}}</ref>。這些體型較小的犬齒獸亞目物種最終僅能去填補那些不用過於和日行性恐龍競爭的生態位，逐漸演化成[[食蟲動物|以昆蟲為食]]的夜行性動物<ref>{{cite book|last1=Kielan-Jaworowska|first1=Zofia|last2=Cifelli|first2=Richard L.|last3=Luo|first3=Zhe-Xi|title=Mammals from the age of dinosaurs : origins, evolution, and structure|url=https://archive.org/details/mammalsfromagedi00kiel_769|date=2004|publisher=Columbia University Press|location=New York|isbn=978-0-231-11918-4|page=[https://archive.org/details/mammalsfromagedi00kiel_769/page/n23 5]}}</ref>。縱使許多現存的演化支於[[中生代|中生代]]時就已經逐漸分化，然而這些早期的哺乳動物依然維持了小體型及夜行性。

[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]晚期的滅絕事件讓哺乳動物得以去填補恐龍留下的生態位，然而在那之後的數百萬年，哺乳動物依舊保持嬌小的體型<ref>{{cite web|last1=Than|first1=K.|title=Rise of Modern Mammals Occurred Long After Dinosaur Demise|url=http://www.livescience.com/7230-rise-modern-mammals-occurred-long-dinosaur-demise.html|publisher=LiveScience|accessdate=24 November 2014|archive-date=2020-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200509105243/https://www.livescience.com/7230-rise-modern-mammals-occurred-long-dinosaur-demise.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖然現今的大型動物幾乎均為哺乳動物，但大多哺乳動物直到現今依然保持夜行性<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Gamberale-Stille|first1=G.|last2=Hall|first2=K. S. S.|last3=Tullberg|first3=B. S.|title=Signals of profitability? Food colour preferences in migrating juvenile blackcaps differ for fruits and insects|journal=Evolutionary Ecology|volume=20|issue=5|pages=479–490|date=10 August 2006|doi=10.1007/s10682-006-0015-y}}</ref>。

==哺乳動物針對夜行性的適應==
[[File:Short-tailed_shrew,_face,_front,_md,_upper_marlboro_2014-06-04-13.15.37_ZS_PMax_(14362614495).jpg|thumb]]的[[感覺毛|感覺毛]]，用於感知獵物、探索環境、以及社交]]
有些哺乳動物的特徵是針對於夜行性生活的適應，包括：

===感官===
* 靈敏的聽覺適應，包括[[耳廓|耳廓]]與[[聽小骨|聽小骨]]
* 敏銳的嗅覺、完整發展的[[鼻甲|鼻甲]]
* 敏感的觸覺，具有[[感覺毛|感覺毛]]<ref name=scholarpedia>{{cite journal | url=http://www.scholarpedia.org/article/Whisking_behavior | title=Vibrissal behaviour and function | journal=Scholarpedia | volume=6 | page=6642 | accessdate=October 29, 2011 | doi=10.4249/scholarpedia.6642 | year=2011 | last1=Grant | first1=Robyn | last2=Mitchinson | first2=Ben | last3=Prescott | first3=Tony | issue=10 | bibcode=2011SchpJ...6.6642P | archive-date=2021-01-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115212143/http://scholarpedia.org/article/Whisking_behavior | dead-url=no }}</ref> 
* 除了高等靈長類外，具有非常大的[[角膜|角膜]]，比起鳥類和爬蟲類具有較差的成像能力<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Hall|first1=M. I.|last2=Kamilar|first2=J. M.|last3=Kirk|first3=E. C.|title=Eye shape and the nocturnal bottleneck of mammals|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences|date=24 October 2012|volume=279|issue=1749|pages=4962–4968|doi=10.1098/rspb.2012.2258|pmid=23097513|pmc=3497252}}</ref>
* 有限的彩色視覺<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Davies|first1=Wayne I. L.|last2=Collin|first2=Shaun P.|last3=Hunt|first3=David M.|title=Molecular ecology and adaptation of visual photopigments in craniates|journal=Molecular Ecology|date=July 2012|volume=21|issue=13|pages=3121–3158|doi=10.1111/j.1365-294X.2012.05617.x|pmid=22650357}}</ref>

===生理學===
* 特別的[[棕色脂肪組織|棕色脂肪組織]]，能快速產生體熱<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Cannon|first1=B.|title=Brown Adipose Tissue: Function and Physiological Significance|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_physiological-reviews_2004-01_84_1/page/277|journal=Physiological Reviews|date=1 January 2004|volume=84|issue=1|pages=277–359|doi=10.1152/physrev.00015.2003|pmid=14715917}}</ref>
* [[粒線體|粒線體]]進行呼吸作用的速率為同等或體型較小的爬蟲類的5-7倍<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Brand|first1=M. D.|last2=Couture|first2=P.|last3=Else|first3=P. L.|last4=Withers|first4=K. W.|last5=Hulbert|first5=A. J.|title=Evolution of energy metabolism. Proton permeability of the inner membrane of liver mitochondria is greater in a mammal than in a reptile.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_biochemical-journal_1991-04-01_275_1/page/81|journal=The Biochemical Journal|date=1 April 1991|volume=275|pages=81–6|pmid=1850242|issue=1|doi=10.1042/bj2750081|pmc=1150016}}</ref>
* 毛髮能協助在寒冷環境或夜晚時維持體溫調節
* 缺乏防範白天[[紫外線|紫外線]]的機制<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Ringvold|first1=Amund|title=Aqueous humour and ultraviolet radiation|journal=Acta Ophthalmologica|date=27 May 2009|volume=58|issue=1|pages=69–82|doi=10.1111/j.1755-3768.1980.tb04567.x|pmid=6773294}}</ref>
* 胎盤動物缺乏需要可見光協助活化的[[光裂合酶|光裂合酶]]，此種酶可於細菌、真菌甚至是大部分其他動物身上發現<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Lucas-Lledó JI, Lynch M | title = Evolution of mutation rates: phylogenomic analysis of the photolyase/cryptochrome family | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-biology-and-evolution_2009-05_26_5/page/1143 | journal = Molecular Biology and Evolution | volume = 26 | issue = 5 | pages = 1143–53 | date = May 2009 | pmid = 19228922 | pmc = 2668831 | doi = 10.1093/molbev/msp029 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Clues from a Somalian cavefish about modern mammals' dark past |url=https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2018/10/181011112444.htm |accessdate=11 October 2018 |work=Science Daily |publisher=Cell Press |date=October 11, 2018 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109042020/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2018/10/181011112444.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===行為===
* 所有基群（至少於[[胎盤動物|胎盤動物]]）的[[晝夜節律|晝夜節律]]與行為模式皆為夜行性<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Gerkema|first1=M. P.|last2=Davies|first2=W. I. L.|last3=Foster|first3=R. G.|last4=Menaker|first4=M.|last5=Hut|first5=R. A.|title=The nocturnal bottleneck and the evolution of activity patterns in mammals|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences|date=3 July 2013|volume=280|issue=1765|pages=20130508|doi=10.1098/rspb.2013.0508|pmid=23825205|pmc=3712437}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Menaker|first1=M.|last2=Moreira|first2=L.F.|last3=Tosini|first3=G.|title=Evolution of circadian organization in vertebrates|journal=Brazilian Journal of Medical and Biological Research|date=March 1997|volume=30|issue=3|pages=305–313|doi=10.1590/S0100-879X1997000300003|pmid=9246228}}</ref>
* 行{{link-en|地穴|Burrow|穴居}}生活以躲避惡劣天氣與日行性掠食者為基群哺乳動物的特徵<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Damiani|first1=R.|last2=Modesto|first2=S.|last3=Yates|first3=A.|last4=Neveling|first4=J.|title=Earliest evidence of cynodont burrowing|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences|date=22 August 2003|volume=270|issue=1525|pages=1747–51|pmid=12965004|doi=10.1098/rspb.2003.2427|pmc=1691433}}</ref>。

